name: Skater Girl, Venice Skatepark, CA, 2021
description: Barefooted local shreddin' Venice Skatepark in LA. What more do ya want? Mamiya 645, 50mm Portra 400 --- Summer in LA, 2021 Visited Southern California to study light and myself. This series is my love letter to one of my favorite towns, Los Angeles. All shot on film.
